title: Hi, I’m James
text:
About Me
I am a student majoring in psychology and computer science at VCU. I have a strong interest in combining these fields to explore how technology can be used to understand and improve mental health. In my free time, I enjoy working on coding projects, learning new programming languages, and staying active through sports and outdoor activities.
